00:53:07,101 --> 00:53:10,776
But these are all good,
hard-working people.

794
00:53:10,854 --> 00:53:13,232
Green, you don't decide who we let go.

795
00:53:14,942 --> 00:53:16,944
You'll just be the one to tell them.

