00:53:26,412 --> 00:53:27,664
Night, guys.

797
00:53:30,374 --> 00:53:32,376
<font color="#808080">TIMOTHY:</font> Oh, why couldn't
the skeleton cross the road?

798
00:53:35,754 --> 00:53:37,301
Why, sweetie?

799
00:53:37,381 --> 00:53:38,849
Because it had no guts.

800
00:53:38,924 --> 00:53:40,267
<font color="#D900D9">(LAUGHING)</font>

