00:59:31,683 --> 00:59:32,684
Oh!

901
00:59:35,061 --> 00:59:36,859
Oh, sweetie.

902
00:59:37,772 --> 00:59:40,616
Oh, it's beautiful. It's amazing.

903
00:59:40,733 --> 00:59:42,030
It's amazing.

904
00:59:44,028 --> 00:59:46,076
Oh, no, no, no.
