00:59:49,200 --> 00:59:53,831
<font color="#808080">CINDY:</font><i> It turns out, Timothy
was Picasso with a pencil.</i>

907
00:59:53,913 --> 00:59:56,211
<font color="#808080">EVETTE:</font><i> So he had
all the qualities you imagined?</i>

908
00:59:56,374 --> 00:59:57,375
<font color="#808080">JIM:</font><i> Oh, yes.</i>

909
00:59:57,625 --> 01:00:00,754
<font color="#808080">CINDY:</font><i> Yeah, well,
including honest to a fault.</i>

910
01:00:00,837 --> 01:00:01,929
<font color="#D900D9">(GASPS)</font>

911
01:00:13,057 --> 01:00:15,310
<i>He couldn't help
