912
01:00:15,393 --> 01:00:16,485
<font color="#808080">JIM:</font><i> Yeah.</i>

913
01:00:16,978 --> 01:00:19,822
It included an unfortunate
thatch of chin hair.

914
01:00:19,897 --> 01:00:20,898
Mmm.

915
01:00:21,107 --> 01:00:23,360
<font color="#D900D9">(BELL RINGING)</font>

