01:01:24,879 --> 01:01:26,176
But you lost your job.

939
01:01:28,174 --> 01:01:29,721
Make sure all the pencils are good.

940
01:01:29,801 --> 01:01:31,678
<font color="#808080">JIM:</font><i> So things were going to get harder.</i>

941
01:01:31,761 --> 01:01:33,479
<i>But at least I still had my job.</i>

942
01:01:33,721 --> 01:01:34,938
<font color="#808080">CINDY:</font><i> Yes, he did.</i>

943
01:01:35,431 --> 01:01:38,150
They go in this box.
They go on a little pencil vacation.

944
01:01:38,226 --> 01:01:39,273
<font color="#808080">CINDY:</font><i> And what did you say about</i>

945
01:01:39,352 --> 01:01:41,070
<i>having Timothy with you that day?</i>

946
01:01:41,145 --> 01:01:42,988
<font color="#808080">JIM:</font><i> - Oh, right.
- That's a lot of trees.</i>

947
01:01:43,731 --> 01:01:45,028
<i>I couldn't help but feel...</i>

948
01:01:45,108 --> 01:01:46,155
Mind if I have one?

949
01:01:46,317 --> 01:01:47,443
<i>...anything was possible.</i>

950
01:01:47,777 --> 01:01:49,192
<font color="#808080">MARTY:</font> You want another one?
You want a yellow one?

951
01:01:49,237 --> 01:01:51,114
We got this... You see, we got a whole...

