1434
01:27:10,131 --> 01:27:15,012
<i>But... But something
unexpected happened.</i>

1435
01:27:15,428 --> 01:27:19,274
<i>A little miracle. And here it is.</i>

1436
01:27:20,600 --> 01:27:22,443
<i>This is a new kind of pencil</i>

